data.title: Forst in Thunstetten - Falstaff
data.meta_description: 84 Falstaff points for the Restaurant Forst in Thunstetten. Whether it\'s a trout fillet from Thörigen or an authentic English Afternoon Tea with delicious homemade scones - the Forst near Thunstetten is the place to feel good and have a good time.
data.text:
Whether it's a trout fillet from Thörigen or an authentic English Afternoon Tea with delicious homemade scones - the Forst near Thunstetten is the place to feel good and have a good time. Since 1904, they have been offering culinary journeys of discovery for all the senses.
